article_title: Aetna Latest Health Insurer To Pare D.C. Lobbyist Amid ACA Challenges

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Amid a flurry of regulatory challenges facing the health insurance industry, Aetna confirmed it’s no longer a member of one of the historically most powerful lobbies in Washington. America’s Health Insurance Plans, known in D.C. circles as “AHIP,” lost in Aetna its second major health plan member in the last year. [...]
